import React from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const PaymentPage = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const handleFinish = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); // Prevent default form behavior const paymentData = { title: document.querySelector("[name='title']").value, name: document.querySelector("[name='name']").value, email: document.querySelector("[name='email']").value, phone: document.querySelector("[name='phone']").value, address1: document.querySelector("[name='address1']").value, address2: document.querySelector("[name='address2']").value, city: document.querySelector("[name='city']").value, state: document.querySelector("[name='state']").value, zip: document.querySelector("[name='zip']").value, country: document.querySelector("[name='country']").value, paymentMethod: document.querySelector("[name='paymentMethod']").value, }; try { const response = await axios.post("http://localhost:5500/payment", paymentData); // Send form data if (response.status === 201) { navigate("/MyOrder"); // Redirect to MyOrder on success } else { console.error("Payment error:", response.data.message); // Log any server errors } } catch (error) { console.error("Error processing payment:", error); // Handle any errors } }; return (
